title: Shoreditch high street evacuated in London as police investigation is underway
text:
Shoreditch high street evacuated in London as police investigation is underway 
The busy London road has been cleared and traffic is being diverted from the area By ELLIE FLYNN SHOREDITCH High Street in London has been evacuated. 
A police investigation is underway and traffic has been diverted from the area.
